Class TreeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
      • model.TreeNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode

    public class TreeNode
extends javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
    Extension of the DefaultMutableTreeNode class. Used as a node in the TreeModel of the Tree class. Represents one table or package from the JSON file which holds the hierarchy of database tables.
    Author:
    Isidora Škulec, Milan Radeta
    See Also:
